---- Changes since 1.130 ----
A separate signature file can now be selected on the Verify Signed File page.
---- Changes since 1.200 ----
Added checkboxes and a button for deleting multiple public keys at once.
---- Changes since 1.300 ----
Email address is automatically detected when setting up a new key.
---- Changes since 1.360 ----
Converted all pages to use the new Webmin UI library, for a more consistent look.
Added text boxes to encryption, decryption, signing and verification pages for working on pasted text.
